Usage: resetPathGroupOptions [-help] [<pathgroupName>] [-early] [-effortLevel]
                             [-late] [-skewingSlackConstraint]
                             [-slackAdjustment] [-slackAdjustmentPriority]
                             [-targetSlack] [-view]

-help                             # Prints out the command usage
<pathgroupName>                   # pathgroup name (string, optional)
-early                            # early mode only  (bool, optional)
-effortLevel                      # effort level option  (bool, optional)
-late                             # late mode only  (bool, optional)
-skewingSlackConstraint           # slack constraint when skewing 
                                  # (bool, optional)
-slackAdjustment                  # slack adjustment option  (bool, optional)
-slackAdjustmentPriority          # slack adjustment priority option 
                                  # (bool, optional)
-targetSlack                      # target slack option  (bool, optional)
-view                             # view set  (bool, optional)